casebody.data:
No. 09-203. Martin Escobar, Petitioner v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 561 U.S. 1001, 130 S. Ct. 3451,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1048,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5173. June 21, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit for further consideration in light of Carachuri-Rosendo v. Holder, 560 U.S. 563, 130 S. Ct. 2577, 177 L. Ed. 2d 68 (2010).
